{"tid":864744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奪14歲男孩童貞 麻辣英語女教師遭判囚10年","createTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:56:09.000Z","uid":23833,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09e9060a6088393875a7f4a221e8b141390b74f4","tid":864744,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"26歲女教師柯托․佛蕾絲（Yaira Tanies Cotto-Flores）在聖羅倫索市（San Lorenzo）的一所中學任教英文科。案情指，2016年3月1日，她帶着班上當時只有14歲的男學生到一起吃飯。吃完飯後，她以贈送禮物為由，將男孩誘騙到酒店房間，並與其發生性關係。事後，她還贈送男孩一些去痘霜（Spot Cream）和一隻手錶作為禮物。其後，這名老師多次向男孩的手機傳送自己的艷照，男孩將照片和其他朋友分享，事件因而曝光，男孩父母隨即報警。 <br />\n<br />\n男孩在作供的時候表示，那次性行為是他的「第一次」，他說：「老師還教我怎樣戴上保險套」。 <br />\n<br />\n佛蕾絲日前在連續9天的庭訊後認罪，陪審團聽完了整宗性侵事件的始末，法官以「蓄意引誘未成年人發生犯罪性行為」判處她入獄10年，並在服刑期滿後接受8年的「監督釋放」。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRVXwohJ1RI3gnBQmf_65HDd9FMo0KCmwEpG0CkiDVKAILSqA4w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRVXwohJ1RI3gnBQmf_65HDd9FMo0KCmwEpG0CkiDVKAILSqA4w&h=11c40ed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75a1b46bbb4ad671043b757a8da49ac21004dd3f","tid":864744,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"97018a168e4e1eeb1f9de44a08928f2ecda14d85","tid":864744,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a1b46bbb4ad671043b757a8da49ac21004dd3f","tid":864744,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"點"},{"pid":"f22c42d4d9acca130d225a156a5ad3baa056ccd4","tid":864744,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:03:41.000Z","msg":"點"},{"pid":"6f19a693725fec01c4e7613de0d477801fe217b9","tid":864744,"uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"大家請記住：<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">連登乞衣樓豬---EDO脆餅#23833<br />\n(被追擊後